###進銷存本機api測試
### 1. 登入取得 Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin1234"
}

###

### 2. 查詢目前商品庫存（記下要進貨的商品 Id）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer c8087ac693f54398a047e800c7323697

###

### 3. 進貨（選一個商品 Id 填入）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/purchases
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer c8087ac693f54398a047e800c7323697

{
  "supplier": "統一企業",
  "note": "測試進貨",
  "details": [
    { "productId": 4, "quantity": 20, "unitPrice": 30 }
  ]
}

###

### 4. 確認庫存有增加
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/4
Authorization: Bearer c8087ac693f54398a047e800c7323697

###

### 5. 銷貨（出 5 件）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer c8087ac693f54398a047e800c7323697

{
  "customer": "測試客戶",
  "note": "測試銷貨",
  "details": [
    { "productId": 4, "quantity": 5, "unitPrice": 35 }
  ]
}

###

### 6. 測試庫存不足（出 9999 件，應被擋）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer c8087ac693f54398a047e800c7323697

{
  "customer": "測試客戶",
  "note": "庫存不足測試",
  "details": [
    { "productId": 4, "quantity": 9999, "unitPrice": 35 }
  ]
}

